                <h1>How to Easily Pair Your AirPods</h1>
                <p>To pair your AirPods, first ensure they are charged and in their case. Open the lid near your iPhone or iPad, then tap "Connect" on the prompted screen. For other devices, activate Bluetooth and press the setup button on the back of the AirPods case until the light flashes white. Select them from the Bluetooth menu to connect.</p>
